**pcap-treasure-hunt**.
## Quick Start

**Requirements:** Docker, Docker Compose.
# 0) Install Python deps
pip install -r requirements.txt

```bash
# 1) Build & run (auto-generates a random flag at startup)
docker compose up --build -d

#    Open the site
#    http://localhost:8082

# 2) Download the PCAP
# analyze in Wireshark or tshark to recover the flag

# 3) Submit your flag
# paste CTF{...} into the web form and check
